SysRestoreDriver
Copyright 2026 Xuhui Jiang

This product is an independently developed Windows kernel-mode volume
filter driver that provides reboot-restore protection through copy-on-write
sector redirection.

The project is built from scratch against the Windows Driver Kit (WDK)
public headers only. It contains no third-party source code and has no
runtime dependencies beyond the Windows kernel libraries shipped with
the WDK (ntoskrnl, hal).
